# Development Commands

## Workspace (Root)

```bash
pnpm install                     # Install all dependencies
pnpm dev                         # Run frontend + backend simultaneously
pnpm build                       # Build all packages
pnpm lint                        # Lint all packages
pnpm test                        # Run all tests
```

## Frontend

```bash
pnpm --filter frontend dev       # Dev server (port: 5173)
pnpm --filter frontend build     # Production build
pnpm --filter frontend preview   # Preview build
pnpm --filter frontend lint      # ESLint
pnpm --filter frontend test      # Run tests
```

## Backend

```bash
pnpm --filter backend start:dev  # Dev server (port: 3000)
pnpm --filter backend build      # Production build
pnpm --filter backend start:prod # Production run
pnpm --filter backend lint       # ESLint
pnpm --filter backend test       # Unit tests
pnpm --filter backend test:watch # Watch mode
pnpm --filter backend test:cov   # Coverage
pnpm --filter backend test:e2e   # E2E tests
```

## Database

```bash
docker-compose up -d                            # Start PostgreSQL
docker-compose down                             # Stop PostgreSQL
pnpm --filter backend migration:generate        # Generate migration
pnpm --filter backend migration:run             # Run migrations
pnpm --filter backend migration:revert          # Revert migration
pnpm --filter backend seed:run                  # Run seed data
```

## Environment Variables

### Backend (.env)

- `PORT=3000`, `NODE_ENV=development`
- `DB_HOST`, `DB_PORT=5432`, `DB_USERNAME`, `DB_PASSWORD`, `DB_DATABASE=ai_chatbot`
- `JWT_SECRET`, `JWT_EXPIRATION=7d`
- `CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173`
- `GEMINI_API_KEY`, `GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash-exp`

### Frontend (.env)

- `VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/v1`
- `VITE_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3000`
